==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From [[εὐχάριστος]] {{GG|2170}}

===Pronunciation===
εὐχαριστέω / eucharisteō / yoo-khar-is-teh'-o

===Verb===
'''εὐχαριστέω'''

# to be grateful, that is, (actually) to express gratitude (towards); specifically to say grace at a meal: - (give) thank (-ful, -s).

